OL,3,CThanksgiving service to be held for
OL,4,Clate former health secretary Jeane
OL,5,CFreeman
OL,7,FA thanksgiving service is to take
OL,8,Fplace in memory of former Scottish
OL,9,Fhealth secretary Jeane Freeman.
OL,11,FMs Freeman died on February 7 aged 72
OL,12,Fafter being diagnosed with cancer in
OL,13,FJanuary.
OL,15,FA former nurse, she was MSP for the
OL,16,FCarrick, Cumnock and Doon Valley
OL,17,Fconstituency from 2016 to 2021 and
OL,18,Fserved as health secretary from 2018
OL,19,Fto 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
