OL,3,CThanksgiving service to be held for
OL,4,Clate former health secretary Jeane
OL,5,CFreeman
OL,7,FA thanksgiving service will take place
OL,8,Fat the University of Glasgow on
OL,9,FSaturday afternoon following a private
OL,10,Fcremation.
OL,12,FThe service will be held in the
OL,13,Funiversity's Bute Hall and will be
OL,14,Flivestreamed online.
OL,16,FTributes were paid to Ms Freeman
OL,17,Fduring a motion of condolence at the
OL,18,FScottish Parliament earlier this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
