OL,3,CThanksgiving service to be held for
OL,4,Clate former health secretary Jeane
OL,5,CFreeman
OL,7,FMs Freeman was appointed as a senior
OL,8,Fcivil servant with the establishment
OL,9,Fof the Scottish Parliament and
OL,10,FScottish Executive in 1999, before
OL,11,Ftaking on a special adviser role to
OL,12,Fthen Labour first minister Jack
OL,13,FMcConnell.
OL,15,FAfter taking a leading role in the
OL,16,Fcampaign group Women for Independence
OL,17,Fduring the 2014 referendum, she joined
OL,18,Fthe SNP and was elected as an MSP at
OL,19,Fthe 2016 election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
