OL,3,CThanksgiving service to be held for
OL,4,Clate former health secretary Jeane
OL,5,CFreeman
OL,7,FMs Freeman then joined the government
OL,8,Fas minister for social security,
OL,9,Fduring which time she established the
OL,10,Fcreation of a social security service
OL,11,Ffor Scotland.
OL,13,FDuring her time as health secretary,
OL,14,Fshe led on Scotland's response to the
OL,15,FCovid pandemic until her retirement in
OL,16,F2021.
